on des blocs tableau et galerie, etc.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Nouvelles API concernant les blocs de l&rsquo;√©diteur sur WordPress 5.3</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Consulter la note de d√©veloppement (en anglais)&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"YZCinvsj27\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/09/24/new-block-apis-in-wordpress-5-3/\">New Block APIs in WordPress 5.3</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;New Block APIs in WordPress 5.3&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/09/24/new-block-apis-in-wordpress-5-3/embed/#?secret=YZCinvsj27\" data-secret=\"YZCinvsj27\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>WordPress 5.3¬†: mise √† jour de l&rsquo;√©diteur concernant les th√®mes </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Consulter la note de d√©veloppement (en anglais)&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"FXR5SBTYlz\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/09/27/block-editor-theme-related-updates-in-wordpress-5-3/\">Block Editor Theme-related updates in WordPress 5.3</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Block Editor Theme-related updates in WordPress 5.3&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/09/27/block-editor-theme-related-updates-in-wordpress-5-3/embed/#?secret=FXR5S